author: Muhammed
message: Know any women considering a career in cybersecurity? Encourage them check out the Women in CyberSecurity (WiCyS) Security Training Scholarship made possible by Google, Bloomberg LP, and Facebook.  The focus of this scholarship is to award WiCyS members who are seeking cybersecurity employment within the next 1.5 years. The program is designed for students and/or career changers!  The multi-stage program includes the SANS Instituteâ€™s world class training and certifications.  Applications are due 2 August 2021. As the scholarship is for WiCyS members, this is an excellent time for aspiring cybersecurity professionals to join the organization.  We need more women in cybersecurity.   Please help spread the word!  Register as a member and apply for the scholarship using this link:  https://www.wicys.org/benefits/security-training-scholarship/

message: Read both books like a buffet ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ else you get bored of it.  Start with the Kimball one I just start am yesterday.  Kimball is called the Father of Data Warehouse because he started the whole Dimension modelling idea stuff.   Use this guide from this blog on how to read the book  https://www.holistics.io/blog/how-to-read-data-warehouse-toolkit/  Though some of the ideas there from my research won't apply again as a result of the advent of MPP & ELT approach to DW but the fundamental knowledge of Dimensional modelling still valid.  So you may need to scheme through some sections

Hello guys  I got an invite to partake in Omdena challenge some weeks back. In the course of the project, I was given a code due to my performance.  The essence of this code is, you stand a better chance of getting an invite to take part in Omdena challenge whenever you apply. All you do is to fill the application form of any project you want to partake. While filling the form, you will see a field "where did you hear about us", just select you were referred to Omdena and enter the code.  Getting selected to take part in Omdena challenge is very competitive, but with the code, you stand a better chance. After several applications and rejections, I got an invite through a member's code. Taking part in the project can boost your profile for better opportunities in the industry, you can include it as part of your work experience. And as you collaborate with other AI engineers and data scientists around the world, you learn more.  If you so wish to take the advantage of joining Omdena collaborators, to develop your skills, get recognised and make an impact, apply for Omdena projects of your choice and use this code HOV7RYSL0QX3FQ.  To know more about Omdena challenge, visit https://omdena.com/projects/#our_challenges  If you have any questions, feel free to ask.  Thanks.

author: Fabiyi Opeyemi
message: *```The Maiden edition of dbt Meetup in Nigeria*```   The Modern Data stack and the rise of Analytics Engineering isn't just some random speculation, instead, it's gradually becoming a highly sought after skill every organization would need to stay relevant in coming years.   Becoming a Data Engineer can be quite tedious with a high learning curve compared to becoming an Analytics Engineer. Fortunately, Data analyst and data scientist are at an advantage as they can easily pick up the AE stack leveraging on their existing Analytics knowledge which would ensure a seemless integration into the Analytics Engineering role.   It's exciting to know that with the advent of an amazing tool like dbt, data analysts and engineers can now build analytics the way engineers build applications.  In the light of this, We are super excited  to announce the start off of dbt meetup here in Nigeria, which is dedicated to helping data analyst and all data professionals own thier analytics engineering workflow _across all industries_   A lot of  interesting conversations related to the data stacks, data operations, data teams, modeling, testing, dashboards, etc. will be happening in the Meetup and it's definitely one you can't afford to miss out on!  Amazing speakers and interesting topics to look forward to include :   ğŸ“Œ Evolution of the Modern Data stack   ğŸ“ŒSetting up a Modern Data stack from Scratch   ğŸ“ŒNavigating the Remote global job market.   Now, register for the maiden edition coming October 14, 2021 in the link below, also share and invite others   https://www.meetup.com/lagos-dbt-meetup/

message: It is not more a news that abouy 50â€“80% of a data scientistâ€™s time is spent wrangling data and making the data in the right format. AS SEEN ON TWITTER   The UK has a visa scheme for people in tech & you qualify if you're any of these:   Data scientists/ engineers   Digital Marketing experts   Experienced UX/UI designers   Cybersecurity experts   Hardware engineers   Experienced front-end developers   Operating systems engineers   DevOps / SysOps engineers Principal software engineers/developers   Artificial Intelligence, Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning experts (AI, NLP, ML)   Experienced video game developers   Experienced Mobile App developers   Experienced back end developers   If you have any of these business skills, you also qualify:   Experience as a commercial/business lead (P&L, growth, sales and distribution strategy) in a digital business   Experience of expanding or growing a significant product-led digital technology business   Sector-specific experience e.g. payment infrastructure in FinTech / international expansion in EdTech etc.   Solution sales experts   Experienced Product Manager   SaaS or enterprise sales leadership for digital services   Solution sales skills performed for a growing B2B digital business (i.e. not big-company experience)   Performance marketing experts, performed in house for digital businesses   Experienced and senior VC or PE analysts with track records of leading investments in digital businesses   Experienced and senior VC or PE analysts with track records of leading investments in digital businesses   Experience as C Suite in a SMEs + (CEO, CMO, CIO) or head of operations for a digital business   There are two options for applicants applying for endorsement by Tech Nation:   Leader (called â€˜exceptional talentâ€™)   Emerging leader (called â€˜exceptional promiseâ€™)   Exceptional promise applicants are likely to be earlier in their career, usually with less than 5 years of experience. You must be able to prove your potential to be a leader through your skills & achievements   Applicants must either:   Meet one mandatory & two optional â€œExceptional Talentâ€ criteriaÂ  below   OR   Meet one mandatory & two optional â€œExceptional Promiseâ€ criteria in below   Exceptional Talent (leader in relevant field)   An applicant evidencing EXCEPTIONAL TALENT must:   show that they have been recognised as a leading talent in the digital technology sector And provide evidence of 2 of the following:   a proven track record for innovation as a founder or senior executive of a product-led digital technology company or as an employee working on a new digital field or concept   proof of recognition for work beyond the applicantâ€™s occupation that contributes to the advancement of the field they have made significant technical.   commercial or entrepreneurial contributions to the field as a founder, senior executive, board member or employee of a product-led digital technology company   they have demonstrated exceptional ability in the field by academic contributions through research published or endorsed by an expert.   Exceptional Promise (potential leader in relevant field)   An applicant evidencing EXCEPTIONAL PROMISE must:   show they have been recognised as having potential to be a leading talent in the digital technology field   And provide evidence of 2 of the following:   at least 1 example of innovation as a founder of a product led digital technology company or as an employee working on a new digital field or concept   at least 1 example of proof of recognition for work beyond the applicantâ€™s occupation that contributes to the advancement of the field.   at least 1 example of significant technical, commercial or entrepreneurial contributions to the field as a founder or employee of a product-led digital technology company   at least 1 example of exceptional ability in the field by academic contributions through research endorsed by an expert.   To apply for endorsement, visit:   https://www.gov.uk/global-talent-digital-technology/apply-for-endorsement   After that, complete a Tech Nation Visa application form for assessment here:   https://tech-nation-visa.smapply.io/prog/tech_nation_visa_application/
